        <!---DNS---->
        <section class="bg-slate-50">
            <div class="container mx-auto py-16">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center py-16 px-5 md:py-28 border bg-white">

                    <div class="relative">
                        <h1 class="head-1 !font-bold mb-2 text-primary px-4">DNS</h1>
                        <p class="body-text1 text-slate-700 max-w-[1120px] px-4 mb-6">The DNS service provides DNS <strong>(PowerDNS)</strong> for all the domains on your LxRoot cluster.</p>

                        <p class="body-text1 text-slate-700 px-4">It is possible to run an LxRoot cluster without installing the DNS service. You can choose to use LxRoot's automatic <strong>CloudFlare</strong> synchronisation or an entirely separate DNS provider.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full py-16 px-4 md:py-16 borders bg-white gap-4">

                
                        <div class="border rounded flex w-48 h-48 items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white">
